subject: HTML
question:
Enter the code to insert an iframe that has these characteristics:

-The source is https://www.google.com.
-500 px of width and height.
-No frameborder.
-Allows full screen.
-Safe content.
answer:
<iframe src="https://www.google.com" width="500" height="500" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen sandbox> 
</iframe>
